Class RabbitHole

java.lang.Object
simulator.objects.NonBlockable
simulator.objects.RabbitHole
All Implemented Interfaces:
NonBlocking
public class RabbitHole extends NonBlockable
The RabbitHole class represents a rabbit hole that rabbits can enter at night. This can also be used to represent a network of connected rabbit holes.
